scene.message:
Trish: Hi!{nl}
I'm Trish!{nl}
This is the Healing Spring!{waitkey}{clearbox}The world runs on{nl}
give and take!{nl}
Money buys any Recovery!{waitkey}{ret}

Trish: Let's see...{nl}
going by recent{nl}
healing rates, for everyone...{waitkey}{ret}

Trish: Thanks!{nl}
Okay, let me heal you up!{nl}
Pain, pain, fly away!{waitkey}{ret}

Trish: Phew...{nl}
That's all!{nl}
You're all better now!{waitkey}{ret}

Trish: Boo~!{nl}
You don't have the money?!{nl}
Trish hates broke people!{waitkey}{clearbox}Come back once you've{nl}
saved up some cash{nl}
bye-bye!{waitkey}{ret}

Trish: Boo~!{nl}
Cheap, cheap, super cheap!{nl}
Don't blame me if you die!{waitkey}{ret}

Come again sometime{nl}
I'll be waiting{nl}
bye-bye!{waitkey}{ret}

Trish: Boo~!{nl}
You called me for nothing?!{nl}
Get out!{waitkey}{ret}
